      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "初始状态需要在Switch上方加一个Note，说明它的MAC表是空的——Tabla MAC vacía。这是ARP学习的起点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Note"
